msgid "🎉 Guild Event Complete!"
msgstr "🎉 ¡Evento del Servidor Completado!"

msgid ""
"The event goal has been reached!\n"
"\n"
"🍬 All participants receive **{reward}** bonus candies!\n"
"*Congratulations!* 🎃"
msgstr ""
"¡Se ha alcanzado la meta del evento!\n"
"\n"
"🍬 ¡Todos los participantes reciben **{reward}** caramelos de bonificación!\n"
"*¡Felicidades!* 🎃"

msgid "That doesn't sound fun."
msgstr "Eso no suena divertido."

msgid "You pretend to eat a candy."
msgstr "Finges comer un caramelo."

msgid "That's not a candy type! Use the inventory command to see what you have."
msgstr "¡Ese no es un tipo de caramelo! Usa el comando de inventario para ver lo que tienes."

msgid "You don't have that many {candy_type}."
msgstr "No tienes tantos {candy_type}."

msgid "You contemplate the idea of eating {candy_type}."
msgstr "Contemplas la idea de comer {candy_type}."

msgid "You leisurely enjoy"
msgstr "Disfrutas tranquilamente de"

msgid "You take the time to savor"
msgstr "Te tomas el tiempo para saborear"

