msgstr "caramelo"

msgid "candies"
msgstr "caramelos"

msgid "🌶️ Ghost Pepper!"
msgstr "🌶️ ¡Pimiento Fantasma!"

msgid ""
"{eat_phrase} {number} ghost {pepper_word}!\n"
"\n"
"🔥 **SPICY!** Your mouth is on fire!\n"
"...but the heat burns away all your sickness!\n"
"💊 Sickness reset to **0**!"
msgstr ""
"{eat_phrase} {number} {pepper_word} fantasma!\n"
"\n"
"🔥 **¡PICANTE!** ¡Tu boca está en llamas!\n"
"...pero el calor quema toda tu enfermedad.\n"
"💊 ¡Enfermedad reseteada a **0**!"

msgid "pepper"
msgstr "pimiento"

msgid "peppers"
msgstr "pimientos"

msgid "After all that candy, sugar doesn't sound so good."
msgstr "Después de tanto caramelo, el azúcar ya no suena tan bien."

msgid ""
"You begin to think you don't need all this candy, maybe...\n"
"*{lost_candy} candies are left behind*"
msgstr ""
"Empiezas a pensar que no necesitas todo este caramelo, quizás...\n"
"*{lost_candy} caramelos se quedan atrás*"

msgid "You feel absolutely disgusted. At least you don't have any candies left."
msgstr "Te sientes completamente asqueado. Al menos no te quedan caramelos."

msgid ""
"You toss your candies on the ground in disgust.\n"
"*{lost_candy} candies are left behind*"
msgstr ""
"Tiras tus caramelos al suelo asqueado.\n"
"*{lost_candy} caramelos se quedan atrás*"

