msgstr "🎃 Página {current}/{total} — Trick or Treat v{version}"

msgid "📖 Guide — How to Play?"
msgstr "📖 Guía — ¿Cómo jugar?"

msgid ""
"Welcome to **Trick or Treat**! 🎃\n"
"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n"
"\n"
"**How to start?**\n"
"Type **`trick or treat`** in an enabled channel to go door-to-door asking for candy. But be careful! You don't always get treats...\n"
"\n"
"**🎁 Treat (75%)** — You receive candy and possible bonus drops.\n"
"**👻 Trick (25%)** — Something bad happens: lose candy, get sick, or both.\n"
"\n"
"**Goal:** Eat as many candies as possible and climb the global leaderboard.\n"
"\n"
"Use `{p}cinventory` to see your inventory and `{p}cboard` for the leaderboard."
msgstr ""
"¡Bienvenido a **Trick or Treat**! 🎃\n"
"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n"
"\n"
"**¿Cómo empezar?**\n"
"Escribe **`trick or treat`** en un canal habilitado para ir de puerta en puerta pidiendo caramelos. ¡Pero ten cuidado! No siempre recibes dulces...\n"
"\n"
"**🎁 Dulce (75%)** — Recibes caramelos y posibles bonus.\n"
"**👻 Truco (25%)** — Algo malo pasa: pierdes caramelos, te enfermas, o ambos.\n"
"\n"
"**Objetivo:** Come tantos caramelos como puedas y sube en la tabla de clasificación.\n"
"\n"
"Usa `{p}cinventory` para ver tu inventario y `{p}cboard` para la tabla."

msgid "🍬 Guide — Candy Types"
msgstr "🍬 Guía — Tipos de Caramelos"

msgid ""
"Each candy type has a special effect when eaten:\n"
"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n"
"\n"
"🍬 **Candies** — The main candy. Eating them increases your *eaten* score, but **also raises sickness** (+2 per candy).\n"
"\n"
"🍫 **Chocolates** — Reduces sickness by **10** per piece. Sweet medicine!\n"
"\n"
"🍭 **Lollipops** — Reduces sickness by **20** per piece. More effective.\n"
"\n"
"🥠 **Cookies** — Sets your sickness to a **random** number (0-100). A gamble!\n"
"\n"
"⭐ **Stars** — Resets your sickness to **0** instantly. The best!\n"
"\n"
"✨ **Golden Candy** — *LEGENDARY*. Worth **10×** in score and **no sickness**.\n"
"\n"
"🌶️ **Ghost Pepper** — *ULTRA RARE*. Resets sickness to **0** when eaten."
msgstr ""
"Cada tipo de caramelo tiene un efecto especial al comerlo:\n"
"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n"
"\n"
"🍬 **Caramelos** — El caramelo principal. Comerlos aumenta tu puntuación de *comidos*, pero **también sube la enfermedad** (+2 por caramelo).\n"
"\n"
"🍫 **Chocolates** — Reduce enfermedad en **10** por unidad. ¡Dulce medicina!\n"
"\n"
"🍭 **Piruletas** — Reduce enfermedad en **20** por unidad. Más efectivas.\n"
"\n"
"🥠 **Galletas** — Establece tu enfermedad en un número **aleatorio** (0-100). ¡Una apuesta!\n"
"\n"
"⭐ **Estrellas** — Resetea tu enfermedad a **0** instantáneamente. ¡La mejor!\n"
"\n"
"✨ **Caramelo Dorado** — *LEGENDARIO*. Vale **10×** en puntuación y **sin enfermedad**.\n"
"\n"
"🌶️ **Pimiento Fantasma** — *ULTRA RARO*. Resetea enfermedad a **0** al comerlo."

msgid "📝 How to eat"
msgstr "📝 Cómo comer"

msgid "💊 Guide — Sickness System"
msgstr "💊 Guía — Sistema de Enfermedad"

msgid ""
"Sickness rises when you eat candies and affects your rewards:\n"
"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n"
"\n"
"😊 **0-40** — Everything normal. No penalty.\n"
"\n"
"😰 **41-80** — You start feeling unwell, but no punishment yet.\n"
"\n"
"🤮 **81-100** — ⚠️ **Rewards halved.** If you were going to get 20 candies, you get 10.\n"
"\n"
"💀 **>100** — ⚠️ **Rewards quartered** + a **50% chance** of **dropping** candies on the ground when trick-or-treating.\n"
"\n"
"**How to cure?**\n"
"🍫 Chocolates (-10) · 🍭 Lollipops (-20) · ⭐ Stars (reset) · 🌶️ Ghost Peppers (reset)\n"
"You also recover a little passively by chatting in ToT channels."
msgstr ""
"La enfermedad sube al comer caramelos y afecta tus recompensas:\n"
"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n"
"\n"
"😊 **0-40** — Todo normal. Sin penalización.\n"
"\n"
"😰 **41-80** — Empiezas a sentirte mal, pero sin castigo aún.\n"
"\n"
"🤮 **81-100** — ⚠️ **Recompensas a la mitad.** Si ibas a recibir 20 caramelos, recibes 10.\n"
"\n"
"💀 **>100** — ⚠️ **Recompensas divididas entre 4** + **50% de probabilidad** de **soltar** caramelos al suelo al hacer trick-or-treat.\n"
"\n"
"**¿Cómo curarse?**\n"
"🍫 Chocolates (-10) · 🍭 Piruletas (-20) · ⭐ Estrellas (reset) · 🌶️ Pimientos Fantasma (reset)\n"
"También te recuperas un poco pasivamente al chatear en canales de ToT."

msgid "💡 Tip"
msgstr "💡 Consejo"

msgid "Don't let sickness go above 80. Buy cures from the shop if you don't get them as bonus drops."
msgstr "No dejes subir la enfermedad por encima de 80. Compra curas en la tienda si no te salen de bonus."

msgid "🏪 Guide — Shop & Shield"
msgstr "🏪 Guía — Tienda y Escudo"

msgid ""
"Spend your candies at the shop to buy useful items:\n"
"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n"
"\n"
"Use `{p}totshop` to browse and `{p}totbuy <item> [amount]` to purchase.\n"
"\n"
"🍫 **Chocolate** — 15 🍬 · Reduces sickness\n"
"🍭 **Lollipop** — 30 🍬 · Reduces more sickness\n"
"🥠 **Cookie** — 25 🍬 · Random sickness\n"
"⭐ **Star** — 50 🍬 · Resets sickness\n"
"🛡️ **Shield** — 75 🍬 · Theft protection\n"
"✨ **Golden Candy** — 200 🍬 · 10× score, no sickness\n"
msgstr ""
"Gasta tus caramelos en la tienda para comprar objetos útiles:\n"
"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n"
"\n"
"Usa `{p}totshop` para ver la tienda y `{p}totbuy <objeto> [cantidad]` para comprar.\n"
"\n"
"🍫 **Chocolate** — 15 🍬 · Reduce enfermedad\n"
"🍭 **Piruleta** — 30 🍬 · Reduce más enfermedad\n"
"🥠 **Galleta** — 25 🍬 · Enfermedad aleatoria\n"
"⭐ **Estrella** — 50 🍬 · Resetea enfermedad\n"
"🛡️ **Escudo** — 75 🍬 · Protección contra robos\n"
"✨ **Caramelo Dorado** — 200 🍬 · 10× puntuación, sin enfermedad\n"

msgid "🛡️ What does the Shield do?"
msgstr "🛡️ ¿Qué hace el Escudo?"

msgid "The shield protects your candy bag from theft via `stealcandy`. It lasts several hours (configurable by admins). You can only have **1 active** at a time."
msgstr "El escudo protege tu bolsa de caramelos contra robos con `stealcandy`. Dura varias horas (configurable por admins). Solo puedes tener **1 activo** a la vez."

msgid "🔥 Guide — Streaks, Stealing & Rare Items"
msgstr "🔥 Guía — Rachas, Robos e Ítems Raros"

msgid ""
"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n"
"\n"
"**🔥 Daily Streaks**\n"
"Play `trick or treat` every consecutive day to build your streak.\n"
"Each streak day adds **×0.1** to your reward multiplier.\n"
"Day 1: ×1.0 · Day 5: ×1.5 · Day 10: ×2.0 · Max: **×3.0**\n"
"Miss a day and the streak resets!\n"
"\n"
"**🗡️ Stealing Candy**\n"
"Use `{p}stealcandy [@user]` to attempt a theft.\n"
"It doesn't always work — there are various success/failure chances.\n"
"The victim receives a **DM notification** when stolen from. 📩\n"
"Buy a **🛡️ Shield** to protect yourself.\n"
"\n"
"**💎 Rare Items**\n"
"When doing `trick or treat`, there's a small chance of getting:\n"
"✨ **Golden Candy** (0.5%) — Worth ×10 when eaten.\n"
"🌶️ **Ghost Pepper** (0.3%) — Resets your sickness.\n"
msgstr ""
"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n"
"\n"
"**🔥 Rachas Diarias**\n"
"Juega `trick or treat` cada día consecutivo para construir tu racha.\n"
"Cada día de racha añade **×0.1** a tu multiplicador de recompensas.\n"
"Día 1: ×1.0 · Día 5: ×1.5 · Día 10: ×2.0 · Máx: **×3.0**\n"
"¡Si fallas un día la racha se resetea!\n"
"\n"
"**🗡️ Robar Caramelos**\n"
"Usa `{p}stealcandy [@usuario]` para intentar un robo.\n"
"No siempre funciona — hay varias probabilidades de éxito/fallo.\n"
"La víctima recibe una **notificación por MD** al ser robada. 📩\n"
"Compra un **🛡️ Escudo** para protegerte.\n"
"\n"
"**💎 Objetos Raros**\n"
"Al hacer `trick or treat`, hay una pequeña probabilidad de obtener:\n"
"✨ **Caramelo Dorado** (0.5%) — Vale ×10 al comerlo.\n"
"🌶️ **Pimiento Fantasma** (0.3%) — Resetea tu enfermedad.\n"

msgid "📋 Guide — Command List"
msgstr "📋 Guía — Lista de Comandos"

msgid "🎮 Player"
msgstr "🎮 Jugador"

msgid ""
"`trick or treat` — Go door to door\n"
"`{p}eatcandy [n] [type]` — Eat candy\n"
"`{p}cinventory` — View your inventory\n"
"`{p}totstats [@user]` — Detailed statistics\n"
"`{p}cboard` — Global eaten leaderboard\n"
"`{p}totshop` — View the shop\n"
"`{p}totbuy <item> [n]` — Buy from the shop\n"
"`{p}buycandy <n>` — Buy candy with bot currency\n"
"`{p}pickup` — Pick up candy from the ground\n"
"`{p}stealcandy [@user]` — Steal candy\n"
"`{p}tothelp` — This guide"
msgstr ""
"`trick or treat` — Ir de puerta en puerta\n"
"`{p}eatcandy [n] [tipo]` — Comer caramelos\n"
"`{p}cinventory` — Ver tu inventario\n"
"`{p}totstats [@usuario]` — Estadísticas detalladas\n"
"`{p}cboard` — Tabla de comidos global\n"
"`{p}totshop` — Ver la tienda\n"
"`{p}totbuy <objeto> [n]` — Comprar de la tienda\n"
"`{p}buycandy <n>` — Comprar caramelos con moneda del bot\n"
"`{p}pickup` — Recoger caramelos del suelo\n"
"`{p}stealcandy [@usuario]` — Robar caramelos\n"
"`{p}tothelp` — Esta guía"

msgid "🔧 Admin / Mod"
msgstr "🔧 Admin / Mod"

msgid ""
"`{p}tottoggle` — Toggle the game on/off\n"
"`{p}totchannel add/remove` — Game channels\n"
"`{p}totcooldown [s]` — Trick or treat cooldown\n"
"`{p}totpickupcooldown [s]` — Pickup cooldown\n"
"`{p}totstealcooldown [s]` — Steal cooldown\n"
"`{p}totshieldhours [h]` — Shield duration\n"
"`{p}totbalance` — Candies in the pool\n"
"`{p}totaddcandies <n>` — Add to pool\n"
"`{p}totgivecandy @user type n` — Give candy\n"
"`{p}totremovecandy @user type n` — Remove candy\n"
"`{p}totevent start/status/stop` — Guild events"
msgstr ""
"`{p}tottoggle` — Activar/desactivar el juego\n"
"`{p}totchannel add/remove` — Canales del juego\n"
"`{p}totcooldown [s]` — Cooldown de trick or treat\n"
"`{p}totpickupcooldown [s]` — Cooldown de pickup\n"
"`{p}totstealcooldown [s]` — Cooldown de steal\n"
"`{p}totshieldhours [h]` — Duración del escudo\n"
"`{p}totbalance` — Caramelos en el pool\n"
"`{p}totaddcandies <n>` — Añadir al pool\n"
"`{p}totgivecandy @user tipo n` — Dar caramelos\n"
"`{p}totremovecandy @user tipo n` — Quitar caramelos\n"
"`{p}totevent start/status/stop` — Eventos del servidor"

msgid "📊 {name}'s Statistics"
msgstr "📊 Estadísticas de {name}"

msgid "🍬 Candy Stats"
msgstr "🍬 Estadísticas de Caramelos"

msgid "🔥 Streaks"
msgstr "🔥 Rachas"

msgid "🎭 Trick or Treat"
msgstr "🎭 Trick or Treat"

msgid "🗡️ Theft Record"
msgstr "🗡️ Registro de Robos"

msgid "💎 Rare Items"
msgstr "💎 Objetos Raros"

msgid "🛡️ Shield"
msgstr "🛡️ Escudo"

msgid "✅ Active ({remaining} left)"
msgstr "✅ Activo ({remaining} restante)"

msgid ""
"This will clear ALL saved data for this cog and reset it to the defaults.\n"
msgstr ""
"Esto borrará TODOS los datos guardados de este cog y los reseteará a los valores por defecto.\n"

msgid "If you are absolutely sure you want to do this, use `{prefix}totclearall yes`."
msgstr "Si estás absolutamente seguro de querer hacer esto, usa `{prefix}totclearall yes`."

msgid "All data for this cog has been cleared."
msgstr "Todos los datos de este cog han sido borrados."

msgid "Trick or treating cooldown time reset to 5m."
msgstr "Cooldown de trick or treat reseteado a 5m."

msgid "Trick or treating cooldown time set to the minimum of 30s."
msgstr "Cooldown de trick or treat establecido al mínimo de 30s."

msgid "Trick or treating cooldown time set to {cooldown_time}s."
msgstr "Cooldown de trick or treat establecido en {cooldown_time}s."

msgid "Pickup cooldown reset to 10m (600s)."
msgstr "Cooldown de pickup reseteado a 10m (600s)."

msgid "Pickup cooldown set to {val}s."
msgstr "Cooldown de pickup establecido en {val}s."

msgid "Steal cooldown reset to 10m (600s)."
msgstr "Cooldown de steal reseteado a 10m (600s)."

msgid "Steal cooldown set to {val}s."
msgstr "Cooldown de steal establecido en {val}s."

msgid "Shield duration reset to 4 hours."
msgstr "Duración del escudo reseteada a 4 horas."

msgid "Shield duration set to {hours} hours."
msgstr "Duración del escudo establecida en {hours} horas."

msgid "You need to wait {remaining}s before picking up candy again."
msgstr "Debes esperar {remaining}s antes de recoger caramelos de nuevo."

msgid "You start searching the area for candy..."
msgstr "Empiezas a buscar caramelos por la zona..."

msgid "There's no candy left on the ground!"
msgstr "¡No quedan caramelos en el suelo!"

msgid "You found {found} 🍬!"
msgstr "¡Encontraste {found} 🍬!"

msgid "You need to wait {remaining}s before stealing again."
msgstr "Debes esperar {remaining}s antes de robar de nuevo."

msgid "No one has any candy yet!"
msgstr "¡Nadie tiene caramelos todavía!"

msgid "You couldn't find anyone to steal from."
msgstr "No pudiste encontrar a nadie a quien robar."

msgid "🛡️ Shield Blocked!"
msgstr "🛡️ ¡Escudo Bloqueó!"

msgid ""
"You tried to steal from **{name}**, but their candy bag\n"
"is protected by a **magical shield**! ✨\n"
"\n"
"Shield expires in: {remaining}"
msgstr ""
"Intentaste robar a **{name}**, pero su bolsa de caramelos\n"
"está protegida por un **escudo mágico**! ✨\n"
"\n"
"El escudo expira en: {remaining}"

msgid "You snuck around for a while but didn't find anything."
msgstr "Merodeaste un rato pero no encontraste nada."

msgid "You see an unsuspecting guildmate..."
msgstr "Ves a un miembro del servidor desprevenido..."

msgid "There was nothing in {user1}'s pockets, so you picked {user2}'s pockets but they had no candy either!"
msgstr "No había nada en los bolsillos de {user1}, así que revisaste los de {user2}, ¡pero tampoco tenía caramelos!"

msgid "There was nothing in {user1}'s pockets, so you looked around again... you saw {user2} in the distance, but you didn't think you could catch up..."
msgstr "No había nada en los bolsillos de {user1}, así que miraste de nuevo... viste a {user2} a lo lejos, pero no creíste poder alcanzarle..."

msgid "You start sneaking around in the shadows..."
msgstr "Empiezas a acechar entre las sombras..."

msgid "You snuck up on {user} and tried picking their pockets but there was nothing there!"
msgstr "Te acercaste sigilosamente a {user} e intentaste robarle, ¡pero no había nada!"

msgid "You start looking around for a target..."
msgstr "Empiezas a buscar un objetivo..."

msgid "You stealthily move over to an unsuspecting person..."
msgstr "Te acercas sigilosamente a una persona desprevenida..."

msgid "You found someone to pickpocket, but they had nothing but pocket lint."
msgstr "Encontraste a alguien a quien robar, pero solo tenía pelusa en los bolsillos."

msgid "You look around furtively..."
msgstr "Miras a tu alrededor furtivamente..."

msgid "You glance around slowly, looking for your target..."
msgstr "Miras lentamente a tu alrededor, buscando tu objetivo..."

msgid "You see someone with a full candy bag..."
msgstr "Ves a alguien con una bolsa llena de caramelos..."

msgid "You creep closer to the target..."
msgstr "Te acercas sigilosamente al objetivo..."

msgid "You hear a sound behind you! When you turn back, your target is gone."
msgstr "¡Escuchas un sonido detrás de ti! Cuando te giras, tu objetivo ha desaparecido."

msgid "You look away for a moment and your target has vanished."
msgstr "Apartas la mirada un momento y tu objetivo ha desaparecido."

msgid "Something flashes in your peripheral vision, and as you turn to look, your target gets away..."
msgstr "Algo destella en tu visión periférica, y cuando te giras a mirar, tu objetivo escapa..."

msgid "There seems to be an unsuspecting victim in the corner..."
msgstr "Parece haber una víctima desprevenida en la esquina..."

msgid "You stole {stolen} 🍬 from {user}!"
msgstr "¡Robaste {stolen} 🍬 de {user}!"

msgid "🗡️ Candy Theft Alert!"
msgstr "🗡️ ¡Alerta de Robo de Caramelos!"

msgid ""
"**{thief}** just stole **{stolen}** 🍬 from your bag!\n"
"\n"
"Remaining candies: **{remaining}** 🍬\n"
"\n"
"*Buy a 🛡️ Shield from the shop to protect yourself!*"
msgstr ""
"**{thief}** acaba de robar **{stolen}** 🍬 de tu bolsa!\n"
"\n"
"Caramelos restantes: **{remaining}** 🍬\n"
"\n"
"*¡Compra un 🛡️ Escudo en la tienda para protegerte!*"

msgid ""
"No active event. Use `{prefix}totevent start <type> <goal>` to start one!\n"
"Event types: {event_types}"
msgstr ""
"No hay evento activo. ¡Usa `{prefix}totevent start <tipo> <meta>` para iniciar uno!\n"
"Tipos de evento: {event_types}"

msgid "🎃 Guild Event — {desc}"
msgstr "🎃 Evento del Servidor — {desc}"

msgid "Invalid event type! Choose from: {types}"
msgstr "¡Tipo de evento inválido! Elige entre: {types}"

msgid "Goal must be positive!"
msgstr "¡La meta debe ser positiva!"

msgid "Reward must be positive!"
msgstr "¡La recompensa debe ser positiva!"

msgid "An event is already active! Use `{prefix}totevent stop` to cancel it first."
msgstr "¡Ya hay un evento activo! Usa `{prefix}totevent stop` para cancelarlo primero."

msgid "🎃 New Guild Event Started!"
msgstr "🎃 ¡Nuevo Evento del Servidor!"

msgid ""
"**{desc}**\n"
"\n"
"{emoji} Goal: **{goal}** candies {event_type}!\n"
"🍬 Reward: **{reward}** candies per participant!\n"
"\n"
"*Everyone's progress counts! Work together!* 🎃"
msgstr ""
"**{desc}**\n"
"\n"
"{emoji} Meta: **{goal}** caramelos {event_type}!\n"
"🍬 Recompensa: **{reward}** caramelos por participante!\n"
"\n"
"*¡El progreso de todos cuenta! ¡Trabajen juntos!* 🎃"

msgid "No active event right now."
msgstr "No hay evento activo ahora mismo."

msgid "No active event to stop."
msgstr "No hay evento activo que detener."

msgid "🎃 Event Cancelled"
msgstr "🎃 Evento Cancelado"

msgid "The guild event has been cancelled."
msgstr "El evento del servidor ha sido cancelado."

msgid ""
"Trick or Treat Channels:\n"
msgstr ""
"Canales de Trick or Treat:\n"

msgid ""
"\n"
"The game toggle for this server is **Off**. Turn it on with the `{prefix}tottoggle` command."
msgstr ""
"\n"
"El juego está **Desactivado** en este servidor. Actívalo con el comando `{prefix}tottoggle`."

msgid "{channel} added to the valid Trick or Treat channels.{toggle_info}"
msgstr "{channel} añadido a los canales válidos de Trick or Treat.{toggle_info}"

msgid "{channel} is already in the list of Trick or Treat channels.{toggle_info}"
msgstr "{channel} ya está en la lista de canales de Trick or Treat.{toggle_info}"

msgid "{channel} not in whitelist."
msgstr "{channel} no está en la lista blanca."

msgid "{channel} removed from the list of Trick or Treat channels."
msgstr "{channel} eliminado de la lista de canales de Trick or Treat."

msgid ""
"Trick or Treating active: {status}.\n"
msgstr ""
"Trick or Treat activo: {status}.\n"

msgid "Trick or Treating channel added: {channel}"
msgstr "Canal de Trick or Treat añadido: {channel}"

msgid "Added {amount} 🍬 to the pool. Now there are {total} 🍬 available to pick up."
msgstr "Se han añadido {amount} 🍬 al pool. Ahora hay {total} 🍬 disponibles para recoger."

msgid "Trick or Treat version {version}"
msgstr "Trick or Treat versión {version}"

msgid "The thought of candy right now doesn't really sound like a good idea."
msgstr "La idea de caramelos ahora mismo no suena como una buena idea."

msgid "All the lights on this street are dark..."
msgstr "Todas las luces de esta calle están apagadas..."

msgid "It's starting to get late."
msgstr "Se está haciendo tarde."

msgid "The wind howls through the trees. Does it seem darker all of a sudden?"
msgstr "El viento aúlla entre los árboles. ¿De repente parece más oscuro?"

msgid "You start to walk the long distance to the next house..."
msgstr "Empiezas a caminar la larga distancia hasta la siguiente casa..."

msgid "You take a moment to count your candy before moving on."
msgstr "Te tomas un momento para contar tus caramelos antes de continuar."

msgid "The house you were approaching just turned the light off."
msgstr "La casa a la que te acercabas acaba de apagar la luz."

msgid "The wind starts to pick up as you look for the next house..."
msgstr "El viento empieza a soplar mientras buscas la siguiente casa..."

msgid "*You hear footsteps...*"
msgstr "*Escuchas pasos...*"

msgid "*You're left alone with your thoughts as you wait for the door to open...*"
msgstr "*Te quedas solo con tus pensamientos mientras esperas a que se abra la puerta...*"

msgid "*The wind howls through the trees...*"
msgstr "*El viento aúlla entre los árboles...*"

msgid "*Does it feel colder out here all of a sudden?*"
msgstr "*¿De repente hace más frío aquí fuera?*"

msgid "*Somewhere inside the house, you hear wood creaking...*"
msgstr "*En algún lugar dentro de la casa, escuchas madera crujiendo...*"

msgid "*You walk up the path to the door and knock...*"
msgstr "*Caminas por el sendero hasta la puerta y tocas...*"

msgid "*You knock on the door...*"
msgstr "*Tocas la puerta...*"

msgid "*There's a movement in the shadows by the side of the house...*"
msgstr "*Hay un movimiento en las sombras al lado de la casa...*"

msgid "*The door slowly opens...*"
msgstr "*La puerta se abre lentamente...*"

msgid "*The ancient wooden door starts to open...*"
msgstr "*La antigua puerta de madera empieza a abrirse...*"

msgid "*A light turns on overhead...*"
msgstr "*Una luz se enciende arriba...*"

msgid "*You hear a scuffling noise...*"
msgstr "*Escuchas un ruido de arrastre...*"

msgid "*There's someone talking inside...*"
msgstr "*Hay alguien hablando dentro...*"

msgid "*The wind whips around your feet...*"
msgstr "*El viento azota tus pies...*"

msgid "*A crow caws ominously...*"
msgstr "*Un cuervo grazna ominosamente...*"

msgid "*You hear an owl hooting in the distance...*"
msgstr "*Escuchas un búho ululando a lo lejos...*"

msgid "💔 Lost **{candy_lost}** candies!"
msgstr "💔 ¡Perdiste **{candy_lost}** caramelos!"

msgid "*Better luck next time...* 👻"
msgstr "*Mejor suerte la próxima vez...* 👻"

msgid "🎃 TRICK! — {name}"
msgstr "🎃 ¡TRUCO! — {name}"

msgid "⚠️ *Sickness penalty: rewards quartered!*"
msgstr "⚠️ *Penalización por enfermedad: ¡recompensas divididas entre 4!*"

msgid "🤮 Too Sick!"
msgstr "🤮 ¡Demasiado Enfermo!"

msgid ""
"You're so sick that you **dropped** {lost} candies!\n"
"\n"
"{face} {bar} **{sickness}**/100\n"
"*Eat chocolate or lollipops to recover!*"
msgstr ""
"¡Estás tan enfermo que se te **cayeron** {lost} caramelos!\n"
"\n"
"{face} {bar} **{sickness}**/100\n"
"*¡Come chocolate o piruletas para recuperarte!*"

msgid "⚠️ *Sickness penalty: rewards halved!*"
msgstr "⚠️ *Penalización por enfermedad: ¡recompensas a la mitad!*"

msgid "Oh, hello. What a cute costume!"
msgstr "Oh, hola. ¡Qué disfraz tan bonito!"

msgid "Look at that costume!"
msgstr "¡Mira ese disfraz!"

msgid "Out this late at night?"
msgstr "¿Fuera a estas horas de la noche?"

msgid "Here's a little something for you."
msgstr "Aquí tienes un detallito."

msgid "The peppermint ones are my favorite."
msgstr "Los de menta son mis favoritos."

msgid "Come back again later if the light is still on."
msgstr "Vuelve más tarde si la luz sigue encendida."

msgid "Go ahead, take a few."
msgstr "Adelante, coge unos cuantos."

msgid "Aww, look at you. Here, take this."
msgstr "Aww, mírate. Toma, llévate esto."

msgid "Don't eat all those at once!"
msgstr "¡No te los comas todos de una vez!"

msgid "Well, I think this is the last of it."
msgstr "Bueno, creo que esto es lo último."

msgid "**Bonus Drops:**"
msgstr "**Bonus Extra:**"

msgid "🌟 **RARE DROPS:**"
msgstr "🌟 **DROPS RAROS:**"

msgid "🎃 TREAT! — {name}"
msgstr "🎃 ¡DULCE! — {name}"
